*   ## **_ROH PURE CHAMPIONSHIP: Lee Moriarty def. Xelhua_**
    

Great match to showcase the very young Xelhua to an international audience. Lee Moriarty continues to reign as longest holder of the ROH Pure Championship of all time.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b208c3c1-f3b7-43dc-a2a6-86e10ecbc5b0/14709.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_QT MARSHALL DEF. PAUL WALTER HAUSER_**
    

He's. A. Wrestler.

Cobra Kai, Fantastic Four and Naked Gun's Paul Walter Hauser just had a FULL ON hardcore match at the ECW Arena with QT Marshall.

Glass, Tables, Golden Globes, Blood, Thumbtacks.

QT Marshall wins when he gives Hauser an avalanche Cutter through a table COVERED IN GLASS

"He's a wrestler" chants for PWH as he receives QTs respect and a standing ovation from Philadelphia

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/177c3d25-f861-49a6-aaa5-90a2c089fc67/14716.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ROH TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: SAMMY GUERVARA AND RUSH DEF. THE OUTRUNNERS_**
    

Sammy Guervara turned heel on the crowd that rejected him a few hours earlier!!

Sammy revealed Dustin Rhodes replacement to be LFI's RUSH!!

Sammy and Rush defeat the Outrunners for the vacant ROH Tag Team Championships then Sammy Guervara joins La Faction Ingobernable

Sammy completes the turn by destroying his former partners, the Von Erichs.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f602357-edf4-43f9-a039-ab5a8cc0611f/14718.jpg?format=original)

