*   ## **_ROH WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: Bandido(c) def. Hechicero_**
    

37 minutes of gourmet professional wrestling. Bandido continues to build one of the most incredible resumes of any wrestler in 2025. Hechicero continues to take advantage of any opportunities he gets in front of this new American audience.

Undoubtedly another Match of the Year contender from ROH World Champion Bandido